269
00:38:55,569 --> 00:38:57,569
Do you have a partner?

270
00:38:57,809 --> 00:39:03,130
More or less. I am not alone
anymore. I don't have a problem.

271
00:39:03,770 --> 00:39:06,650
I hope you were not offended
by my question.

272
00:39:12,291 --> 00:39:14,371
Was her father here?

273
00:39:15,451 --> 00:39:17,811
He asked me if I am a fag.

274
