427
00:55:16,755 --> 00:55:19,075
I would like to,
but she can't hear me.

428
00:55:19,315 --> 00:55:21,915
How are you so certain
about this?

429
00:55:21,995 --> 00:55:25,116
Her brain is dead, Benigno.

430
00:55:25,476 --> 00:55:29,316
The woman's mind is a mystery,
especially in such sickness.

431
00:55:29,756 --> 00:55:33,517
You must look after the woman,
talk to her...

432
00:55:33,637 --> 00:55:37,557
...don't forget that she's alive
and that you love her.

433
00:55:37,607 --> 00:55:41,678
This is the only therapy.
I know from experience.

434
00:55:43,198 --> 00:55:46,158
And what do you know
about women?

435
00:55:46,638 --> 00:55:50,479
Benigno, what do you know
about women?

436
00:55:54,759 --> 00:55:57,829
What do you know about women?

437
00:55:57,879 --> 00:56:02,400
A lot. 20 years next to one,
4 with another.

438
00:56:04,320 --> 00:56:08,320
I like the bullfighter's boyfriend.
He has style.

439
00:56:08,370 --> 00:56:11,231
How do you know? You saw him?

440
00:56:11,281 --> 00:56:15,401
Of course not, but I can tell
from his face.

441
00:56:15,801 --> 00:56:18,682
And his bulging trousers.

442
00:56:21,562 --> 00:56:24,202
He is a good friend of
Benigno, right;

443
00:56:25,962 --> 00:56:30,563
