carry on talking crap about him.

450
00:56:57,366 --> 00:57:01,006
- She likes Benigno.
- She is not in her senses.

451
00:57:07,047 --> 00:57:10,087
I have the day off.
I am going to the film library.

452
00:57:10,137 --> 00:57:13,127
- Are you coming?
