476
01:01:04,352 --> 01:01:07,913
Don't worry, my love!
I will find the antidote!

477
01:01:15,754 --> 01:01:17,744
Time was passing by...

478
01:01:17,794 --> 01:01:20,754
...but Amparo couldn't find
the antidote...

479
01:01:21,074 --> 01:01:24,475
