01:01:32,715 --> 01:01:35,226
So that Amparo doesn't suffer...

482
01:01:35,276 --> 01:01:38,996
...Alfredo leaves and goes
to find his mother.

483
01:01:39,116 --> 01:01:42,277
He hadn't seen her for 10 years,
beacause he was lousy.

484
01:01:42,757 --> 01:01:46,357
He hadn't told Ambaro
where his mother lived.

485
01:01:46,637 --> 01:01:50,037
Lots of things going on
in this movie.

486
01:01:50,477 --> 01:01:53,238
But the most important
thing is...

487
01:01:53,878 --> 01:01:58,158
...after years full of
regrets and studies...

488
01:01:59,318 --> 01:02:03,559
...Amparo finds the address
of his mother.

489
01:02:05,639 --> 01:02:08,199
And goes there.

490
01:02:52,524 --> 01:02:55,684
Hotel Yukali.
Room 15.

491
01:03:22,367 --> 01:03:25,648
- Sleep, my darling.
- And what if I be a burden by mistake?

492
01:05:51,103 --> 01:05:53,424
And Alfredo...

493
01:05:55,824 --> 01:05:58,664
...stays inside her...

494
01:06:01,345 --> 01:06:03,705
...for ever.

495
01:06:24,067 --> 01:06:28,107
AFTER ONE MONTH

496
01:06:29,148 --> 01:06:33,148
Come on, put your hands
correctly... This way...

497
01:06:38,709 --> 01:06:41,829
It's quite cool...
It's great...

498
01:06:42,229 --> 01:06:45,229
It's nice here by
the balcony, right?

499
01:06:45,469 --> 01:06:48,550
Lydia likes to sit by
the balcony as well.

500
01:06:49,310 --> 01:06:51,830
Did you hear that?
She likes it a lot.

501
01:06:52,510 --> 01:06:56,630
Look at them... It's as if
they are talking about us.

502
01:06:58,711 --> 01:07:01,031
What do you think they say?

503
01:07:01,751 --> 01:07:04,261
They have no shame.

504
01:07:04,311 --> 01:07:07,672
Women talk about everything
with each other.

505
01:07:08,952 --> 01:07:12,912
Lydia would tell her she has
completed two months of sickness.

506
01:07:48,356 --> 01:07:50,626
Benjamin and Angela...

507
01:07:50,676 --> 01:07:54,797
...will you bond in marriage,
with your own will?

508
01:07:57,917 --> 01:08:01,558
Join your hands together...

509
01:08:01,918 --> 01:08:06,038
...and declare your wish
in front of God.

510
01:08:10,278 --> 01:08:13,279
I, Angela,
take you, Benjamin...

511
01:08:13,759 --> 01:08:16,919
...to be my lawful husband...

512
01:08:17,279 --> 01:08:20,920
I will love you
in happiness and in sickness...

513
01:08:21,400 --> 01:08:25,480
...so long as we shall both live.

514
01:08:26,720 --> 01:08:29,921
The Lord that joined you in love...

515
01:08:30,201 --> 01:08:34,401
...let him accept your declaration
of love today.

516
01:08:34,801 --> 01:08:38,482
May your love last eternally.

517
01:08:39,042 --> 01:08:42,282
What are you doing here? We
were gonna meet at the hotel.

518
01:08:42,362 --> 01:08:46,402
I changed my mind.
I've always liked weddings.

519
01:08:46,682 --> 01:08:49,963
Weren't you gonna see
your sister before the game?

520
01:08:50,203 --> 01:08:53,113
I called her.
She will come to the hotel.

521
01:08:53,163 --> 01:08:56,363
I promised her we will eat at
the restaurant tonight.

522
01:08:56,413 --> 01:08:58,284
As you wish.

523
01:09:03,044 --> 01:09:06,805
- Nice ceremony, right?
- Excellent.

524
01:09:09,885 --> 01:09:13,885
- I didn't expect her so young.
- You don't trust me right?

525
01:09:14,805 --> 01:09:18,166
We can't have another day
passing by without talking.

526
01:09:18,526 --> 01:09:22,646
Don't worry. Finish with Angela,
I have proof.

527
01:09:23,206 --> 01:09:27,087
For example, at the ceremony
I didn't cry, you did.

528
01:09:27,137 --> 01:09:29,927
- Right.
- And you shouldn't have.

529
01:09:30,087 --> 01:09:32,127
Don't you believe me?

530
01:09:32,407 --> 01:09:36,568
I needed 10 years to get over
it. I finally made it.

531
01:09:38,728 --> 01:09:41,728
Lydia, trust me,
it's over.

532
01:09:42,448 --> 01:09:44,839
I travelled with Angela.

533
01:09:44,889 --> 01:09:48,409
The excuse was to write
a travel guide.

534
01:09:48,769 --> 01:09:53,130
In reality, I wanted her
out of Madrid and drugs.

535
01:09:53,530 --> 01:09:57,770
Madrid is hell. Our relationship
functioned outside it.

536
01:09:58,530 --> 01:10:02,131
After five trips,
I brought her to her parents...

537
01:10:02,181 --> 01:10:06,211
...who kept her away
from drugs and from me.

538
01:10:06,811 --> 01:10:08,851
Did you still love her?

539
01:10:10,451 --> 01:10:14,452
I cried not being able to share
things with her.

540
01:10:15,452 --> 01:10:19,412
It's terrible to leave
a person you love so much.

541
01:10:20,092 --> 01:10:22,293
What a sad story!

542
01:10:22,893 --> 01:10:26,373
Love is a sad thing when
it ends...

543
01:10:26,423 --> 01:10:28,813
...as the song says.

544
01:10:29,173 --> 01:10:31,814
Marco, we need to talk afterwards.

545
01:10:32,094 --> 01:10:35,974
- We've been talking for an hour.
- You have, not me.

546
01:10:36,694 --> 01:10:38,654
You're right.

547
01:11:04,097 --> 01:11:07,298
My leg needs two months of therapy,
said the doctor.

548
01:11:07,618 --> 01:11:10,578
But you know what? I am glad
that bull hit me.

549
01:11:11,018 --> 01:11:14,258
Now I can stay with you until
you wake up.

550
01:11:14,308 --> 01:11:16,699
No one will take me away from you.

551
01:11:18,339 --> 01:11:21,579
We got back together,
a month ago...

552
01:11:22,899 --> 01:11:26,700
Lydia would tell you at the
wedding. She didn't in the end.

553
01:11:29,420 --> 01:11:32,140
It was you she cried for.

554
01:11:34,341 --> 01:11:38,701
She called me to tell me
she cried for me.

555
01:11:40,101 --> 01:11:42,811
Last time we spoke.

556
01:11:42,861 --> 01:11:46,222
Now that I don't fight
due to injury...

557
01:11:46,342 --> 01:11:49,382
...I would like to stay
near her during the night.

558
01:11:49,432 --> 01:11:51,662
Like at your place.

559
01:12:27,946 --> 01:12:30,347
I am alone again.

560
01:12:34,467 --> 01:12:36,937
You were looking at her breasts.

561
01:12:36,987 --> 01:12:40,068
Difficult to avoid it.
They grow by the day.

562
01:12:40,388 --> 01:12:44,868
Benigno, I am thinking of taking
a trip... I have to work.

563
01:12:45,308 --> 01:12:47,348
And Lydia?

564
01:12:47,868 --> 01:12:50,269
She doesn't need me anymore.

565
01:12:52,189 --> 01:12:54,189
Did you break up?

566
01:12:55,109 --> 01:12:57,980
You can call it that.

567
01:12:58,030 --> 01:13:01,990
I expected this, Marco.
Don't ask why, I just did.

568
01:13:03,510 --> 01:13:08,031
There was something in your
relationship that didn't function right.

569
01:13:08,351 --> 01:13:10,341
When are you going?

570
01:13:10,391 --> 01:13:13,271
Soon, but I'll see you before
I go.

571
01:13:13,551 --> 01:13:15,911
I am so sorry you are going.

572
01:13:20,672 --> 01:13:23,632
I am leaving, Benigno.
I'll see you soon.

573
01:13:25,913 --> 01:13:29,473
She didn't have her period yet?

574
01:13:30,913 --> 01:13:34,874
I am looking at the month's report.
She should have had it.

575
01:13:36,194 --> 01:13:38,554
Yes, it's a bit late.

576
01:13:50,315 --> 01:13:54,196
Two weeks. That's a lot.
Are you sure she had it last month?

577
01:13:54,836 --> 01:13:58,956
I personally dealt with it.
It was when you had the flu.

578
01:14:00,116 --> 01:14:02,397
She seems a bit swollen.

579
01:14:02,797 --> 01:14:05,187
They often have abnormalities.

580
01:14:05,237 --> 01:14:08,517
For example, Lydia
doesn't have a period anymore.

581
01:14:08,997 --> 01:14:12,598
Anyway, we should tell Dr Vega.

582
01:14:30,440 --> 01:14:34,040
I brought some of my guides
for Alicia and you.

583
01:14:35,720 --> 01:14:38,040
I said goodbye to Lydia.

584
01:14:39,561 --> 01:14:43,761
I went to see Alicia, but they
didn't let me enter the room.

585
01:14:45,681 --> 01:14:47,841
Is there something wrong?

586
01:14:48,241 --> 01:14:51,202
No. Just some infection
that Alicia got.

587
01:14:51,402 --> 01:14:54,422
Can you drive me home?
I am done with work.

588
01:14:54,472 --> 01:14:57,392
- It's not serious, I hope.
- I don't know.

589
01:14:57,442 --> 01:15:01,363
They do some medical examinations,
but they haven't told me anything.

590
01:15:02,363 --> 01:15:05,353
Brazil...

591
01:15:05,403 --> 01:15:07,644
...Turkey, Cuba.

592
01:15:08,484 --> 01:15:11,564
- I will read them to Alicia.
- They are guides.

593
01:15:12,004 --> 01:15:14,794
Yours. They must be good.

594
01:15:14,844 --> 01:15:17,365
- Are you travelling alone?
- Yes.

595
01:15:17,645 --> 01:15:20,685
I would like to talk to you
about this before you go.

596
01:15:21,005 --> 01:15:24,165
- About what?
- Loneliness.

597
01:15:24,325 --> 01:15:26,606
I want to get married.

598
01:15:29,126 --> 01:15:32,166
- Alicia, of course!
- Benigno, you are nuts!

599
01:15:32,216 --> 01:15:35,157
We will get along better than
most couples.

600
01:15:35,207 --> 01:15:38,447
- Why shouldn't I marry her?
- Because she is in a coma!

601
01:15:40,127 --> 01:15:43,687
Because she can't say 'yes'
in the church!

602
01:15:44,087 --> 01:15:47,648
Because, she is virtually dead!

603
01:15:47,698 --> 01:15:49,438
Get in the car!

604
01:15:49,488 --> 01:15:51,928
- What are you talking about?
- Get in the car!

605
01:15:57,929 --> 01:16:01,369
Your relationship with Alicia
is a crazy monologue!

606
01:16:01,649 --> 01:16:05,170
We often talk to PVS,
but we don't marry them.

607
01:16:05,730 --> 01:16:09,570
Incredible what you are saying.
I had a different opinion of you.

608
01:16:09,850 --> 01:16:13,371
Don't say or think about it
ever again!

609
01:16:13,931 --> 01:16:18,531
Promise!... If you say that to
anyone else, you will be in trouble!

610
01:16:20,611 --> 01:16:23,572
If that calms you down,
then I promise.

611
01:16:23,812 --> 01:16:26,852
- Regardless of how much you like her...
- You like her too, right?

612
01:16:26,902 --> 01:16:28,932
Of course I like her.

613
01:16:29,492 --> 01:16:33,273
- She likes you too.
- She is virtually dead!

614
01:16:33,323 --> 01:16:37,053
She has no feelings about me,
you, or herself!

615
01:16:37,103 --> 01:16:39,573
Understand that!

616
01:16:44,574 --> 01:16:48,114
Our patient Alicia Roncero
was raped and is pregnant.

617
01:16:48,164 --> 01:16:51,655
Before I tell her father
I want you to tell me...

618
01:16:51,705 --> 01:16:54,695
...which bastard did it!

619
01:16:54,745 --> 01:16:57,005
Everyone is upset.

620
01:16:57,055 --> 01:17:00,736
You are responsible. Alicia
was on your floor.

621
01:17:01,016 --> 01:17:04,176
Then allow me to explain the
situation.

622
01:17:04,776 --> 01:17:06,976
Rosa, please.

623
01:17:08,137 --> 01:17:11,897
Alicia's period stopped
two months ago.

624
01:17:12,257 --> 01:17:16,257
I thought it was one month
initially, but I was wrong.

625
01:17:16,457 --> 01:17:19,498
It wasn't in last month's report.

626
01:17:19,698 --> 01:17:22,698
It says it was dealt with normally.

627
01:17:22,938 --> 01:17:26,139
I was down with flu
during that week.

628
01:17:27,099 --> 01:17:30,059
You wrote that.
Right, Benigno?

629
01:17:30,299 --> 01:17:33,339
- It is your typewriting.
- Yes, it was me.

630
01:17:33,539 --> 01:17:36,380
Why did you lie?

631
01:17:36,900 --> 01:17:39,290
I didn't want it to become a problem.

632
01:17:39,340 --> 01:17:42,780
On other occasions, the patients'
periods have also stopped.

633
01:17:44,020 --> 01:17:47,981
How come no one noticed?
Where is the night person?

634
01:17:48,181 --> 01:17:51,381
She can't come today.
She phoned.

635
01:17:51,461 --> 01:17:53,571
Didn't see notice anything strange?

636
01:17:53,621 --> 01:17:57,822
She has problems at home.
A lot of nights she doesn't come.

637
01:17:58,062 --> 01:18:00,622
And who replaces her?

638
01:18:04,143 --> 01:18:07,183
I will tell Roncero
that his daughter...

639
01:18:07,543 --> 01:18:10,343
...is day and night with
a nutcase?

640
01:18:10,423 --> 01:18:12,584
Lets calm down for a bit.

641
01:18:14,224 --> 01:18:19,264
Benigno, do you realise you
are the prime suspect?

642
01:18:20,144 --> 01:18:23,175
Why did you hide the first delay?

643
01:18:23,225 --> 01:18:27,425
What explanation do you have?
Would you ever harm Alicia?

644
01:18:27,665 --> 01:18:29,545
Definitely not!

645
01:18:34,946 --> 01:18:37,656
Last night I was
at the parking lot...

646
01:18:37,706 --> 01:18:41,507
...and overheard a discussion
between Benigno and Marco.

647
01:18:41,627 --> 01:18:44,987
Benigno said he wanted to
marry Alicia.

648
01:18:45,387 --> 01:18:49,187
Marco tried to change his mind,
but in vain.

649
01:18:51,988 --> 01:18:54,298
Lots of couples, he said...

650
01:18:54,348 --> 01:18:57,668
...don'r get along
as well as him and Alicia.

651
01:18:59,749 --> 01:19:03,229
JORDANIA, AFTER EIGHT MONTHS

652
01:19:18,951 --> 01:19:22,871
It was Lydia Gonzales' funeral
yesterday, at Almudena.

653
01:19:24,031 --> 01:19:29,272
The thirty-year old bullfighter
was in a coma since...

654
01:19:32,312 --> 01:19:34,812
Can I speak with
Benigno Martin?

655
01:19:34,862 --> 01:19:37,313
He doesn't work here anymore.

656
01:19:38,393 --> 01:19:40,633
- Are you sure?
- Positive.

657
01:19:40,993 --> 01:19:43,513
- And sister Rosa Lazaga;
- Who are you?

658
01:19:43,563 --> 01:19:46,034
- Marco Zuloaga.
- I will put you through.

659
01:19:50,354 --> 01:19:53,314
- Who is it?
- Marco Zuloaga.

660
01:19:54,195 --> 01:19:57,235
I am calling from Jordan.
I found out about Lydia.

661
01:19:57,285 --> 01:19:59,675
I am sorry, Marco.

662
01:20:00,315 --> 01:20:02,675
You should have called me.

663
01:20:04,076 --> 01:20:06,476
We had a lot of problems here.

664
01:20:06,716 --> 01:20:09,836
What happened? Benigno isn't
there anymore, I was told.

665
01:20:10,276 --> 01:20:13,317
Benigno is in jail.

666
01:20:16,157 --> 01:20:19,797
He is accused of raping Alicia.

667
01:20:22,238 --> 01:20:25,278
Help him. He has no one
the poor guy.

668
01:20:25,328 --> 01:20:27,268
Did you go see him?

669
01:20:27,318 --> 01:20:30,118
After what he did, I can't.

670
01:20:30,358 --> 01:20:33,519
However he does need help,
and you are his friend.

671
01:20:33,719 --> 01:20:37,079
- What prison is he in?
- In Zegovia.

672
01:21:25,924 --> 01:21:28,445
Wait for me here.

673
01:21:43,246 --> 01:21:46,607
- I want to see a prisoner.
- In the visting section.

674
01:21:46,657 --> 01:21:49,047
Through this door, on the left.

675
01:21:59,888 --> 01:22:02,838
I want prisoner Benigno Martin.

676
01:22:02,888 --> 01:22:05,889
It isn't a visting day,
but I will see whether...

677
01:22:05,939 --> 01:22:08,009
I am sorry, I can't hear you.

678
01:22:09,169 --> 01:22:11,479
It isn't a visiting day.

679
01:22:11,529 --> 01:22:15,330
And the lodger didn't ask
for a visit.

680
01:22:15,810 --> 01:22:18,930
He doesn't know I am in Madrid.
I came today.

681
01:22:19,330 --> 01:22:22,571
- Are you a relative?
- A friend.

682
01:22:22,691 --> 01:22:26,371
- Marco Zuloaga is my name.
- Can I see your I.D.?

683
01:22:29,131 --> 01:22:32,932
- Can I call him?
- He will call you.

684
01:22:33,212 --> 01:22:36,692
I have changed number. Can you
give him the new one?

685
01:22:45,613 --> 01:22:47,603
And remember.

686
01:22:47,653 --> 01:22:50,934
Visiting days are Saturday
and Sunday.

687
01:22:51,254 --> 01:22:55,054
But the lodger should ask for
the visit.

688
01:22:55,334 --> 01:22:58,454
If he doesn't want to see you,
there is nothing we can do.

689
01:22:59,935 --> 01:23:03,895
And something else. We don't
have prisoners here...

690
01:23:04,895 --> 01:23:09,176
We don't have prisoners here,
we have lodgers.

691
01:23:44,619 --> 01:23:46,900
Marco, is that you?

692
01:23:47,780 --> 01:23:51,980
I am glad to hear your voice.
I asked your visit on Saturday.

693
01:23:54,340 --> 01:23:56,581
- Where are you?
- Outside the clinique.

694
01:23:58,661 --> 01:24:02,581
Dr Vega told me everything.
How could you do it?

695
01:24:03,221 --> 01:24:06,342
Did you come back to Spain
to get on my back?

696
01:24:07,622 --> 01:24:10,582
Do you need anything?
What should I bring you on Saturday?

697
01:24:10,662 --> 01:24:14,183
I need information.
What do you know about Alicia?

698
01:24:14,233 --> 01:24:16,423
They wouldn't say anything
from the clinique.

699
01:24:16,743 --> 01:24:18,863
She is in a different one.
They don't know where.

700
01:24:18,983 --> 01:24:21,763
- I don't believe this.
- Neither do I.

701
01:24:21,813 --> 01:24:24,544
But I am not surpised they
won't tell us.

702
01:24:24,824 --> 01:24:28,264
- Are you still my friend?
- Of course. Since I am here.

703
01:24:28,464 --> 01:24:30,664
Then find out about Alicia.

704
01:24:31,064 --> 01:24:34,345
Whether she's alive, whether she gave
birth, whether the baby is alive...

705
01:24:34,545 --> 01:24:38,225
I need to know, Marco...
You understand, right?

706
01:24:40,665 --> 01:24:45,106
I will try to...
Talk to you on Saturday...

707
01:24:47,106 --> 01:24:50,627
- Did you find out anything?
- I will. Be patient.

708
01:24:50,947 --> 01:24:56,067
I was, until the day she would
give birth. One month ago.

709
01:24:56,747 --> 01:24:59,027
You must wait.

710
01:25:04,988 --> 01:25:09,189
- What do you do during the day here?
- I work in the recovery room.

711
01:25:09,909 --> 01:25:14,349
It's a new prison, few people.
It's quiet in here.

712
01:25:14,949 --> 01:25:18,310
- It doesn't look like a prison from outside.
- The problem is elsewhere!

713
01:25:18,750 --> 01:25:21,630
That I don't see Alicia.

714
01:25:22,310 --> 01:25:26,270
The doctor  Dr Roncero
say I am a psychopath.

715
01:25:29,591 --> 01:25:33,391
This is good for the trial, they say,
but I don't care about the trial.

716
01:25:33,791 --> 01:25:37,672
I need to see Alicia,
to find out how everything went.

717
01:25:38,312 --> 01:25:42,352
If this goes on, I don't
know what I am capable of doing!

718
01:25:42,592 --> 01:25:44,752
I am a psychopath, they say?
Then I will act like one!

719
01:25:44,802 --> 01:25:46,673
Don't say that, Benigno!

720
01:25:47,833 --> 01:25:52,033
And find me another lawyer.
The one I have despises me.

721
01:25:54,553 --> 01:25:58,594
I will rent my place so that
I can pay him.

722
01:25:59,034 --> 01:26:02,174
I will rent it.
I am currently homeless.

723
01:26:02,224 --> 01:26:05,315
Great. I am glad you will be
my tenant.

724
01:26:06,075 --> 01:26:09,995
I was thinking about you a lot,
especially during the nights.

725
01:26:10,755 --> 01:26:14,116
- Why during the nights?
- Because I study during the nights.

726
01:26:14,356 --> 01:26:17,036
I read all your guides.

727
01:26:17,196 --> 01:26:20,756
Like travelling with you
next to me...

728
01:26:20,806 --> 01:26:23,157
...telling me things.

729
01:26:23,437 --> 01:26:26,477
I liked Avan's the most.

730
01:26:26,717 --> 01:26:28,957
I became one with those people...

731
01:26:29,037 --> 01:26:32,078
...that have nothing
and invent everything.

732
01:26:33,038 --> 01:26:36,078
And you describing
the Cuban girl...

733
01:26:36,128 --> 01:26:39,118
...in front of her window
by the sea...

734
01:26:39,168 --> 01:26:41,158
...waiting in vain...

735
01:26:41,639 --> 01:26:44,719
...for something that will
never happen.

736
01:26:45,319 --> 01:26:48,279
I was thinking that woman is me.

737
01:27:06,281 --> 01:27:09,442
Good morning. I am Benigno's
friend.

738
01:27:09,962 --> 01:27:12,682
You are Marco, the Argentinian?

739
01:27:13,042 --> 01:27:17,682
Benigno called me.
Will you take his appartment?

740
01:27:18,483 --> 01:27:22,723
It will be dirty. He wouldn't
let me in to clean it.

741
01:27:24,163 --> 01:27:28,124
- And I didn't want any money...
- It's OK, I will take care of it.

742
01:27:28,404 --> 01:27:32,044
Shall I give you the key?...
I will go look for it...

743
01:27:38,525 --> 01:27:40,525
Did you see him?

744
01:27:41,605 --> 01:27:44,365
- How is he?
- Well.

745
01:27:45,565 --> 01:27:49,486
Poor guy, he wasn't even lucky
during his imprisonment.

746
01:27:49,536 --> 01:27:51,636
No publicity!

747
01:27:51,686 --> 01:27:55,807
No TV, no reporters.
No one came here.

748
01:27:56,287 --> 01:27:59,447
They didn't condescend!
And they show such garbage!

749
01:27:59,497 --> 01:28:01,527
I would give them an interview!

750
01:28:01,767 --> 01:28:04,287
The media is shit in this country!

751
01:28:04,447 --> 01:28:06,368
You are right.

752
01:28:06,848 --> 01:28:08,888
The keys...

753
01:28:09,448 --> 01:28:13,849
Anyway... Do you know why
Benigno is in prison?

754
01:28:14,289 --> 01:28:18,409
He is very quiet. He didn't say
a word last time he came.

755
01:28:18,969 --> 01:28:21,929
- Benigno is innocent.
- Yes, I know.

756
01:28:22,169 --> 01:28:25,090
- Innocent about what?
- I don't know.

757
01:28:25,450 --> 01:28:28,570
You do, but you don't want
to tell me.

758
01:28:33,531 --> 01:28:36,931
If you need something,
you know where I am.

759
01:30:30,543 --> 01:30:34,344
I was glad you stepped in
by yourself today, without crutches.

760
01:30:36,784 --> 01:30:39,544
- How did the exercise go today?
- Very well.

761
01:30:39,594 --> 01:30:41,654
- Were you tired?
- A lot.

762
01:30:41,704 --> 01:30:45,185
It doesn't matter. We will
do some extra exercises.

763
01:30:46,425 --> 01:30:49,105
We will do some stretches.

764
01:30:49,425 --> 01:30:53,106
- But I already did 100.
- We'll do a few more.

765
01:31:28,670 --> 01:31:31,350
I have an appointment with
Mr. Sainz.

766
01:31:35,670 --> 01:31:38,511
The boy was born dead.

767
01:31:38,631 --> 01:31:41,771
Alicia recovered.
Benigno hasn't found out.

768
01:31:41,821 --> 01:31:44,911
In his condition,
he could do something crazy.

769
01:31:45,351 --> 01:31:49,032
I can't lie to him.
He is my only friend.

770
01:31:49,512 --> 01:31:52,902
I will tell him.
I have no problem.

771
01:31:52,952 --> 01:31:56,473
Alicia is still in coma and
the baby dead, I will say.

772
01:31:56,673 --> 01:31:59,463
But you don't tell him anything.

773
01:31:59,513 --> 01:32:04,113
- Can he bail out?
- Very difficult, and expensive.

774
01:32:31,636 --> 01:32:34,267
- You are wet.
- A little.

775
01:32:34,317 --> 01:32:38,957
Be careful not to catch a cold.
Drink hot milk with honey.

776
01:32:50,158 --> 01:32:53,919
Since I am here,
I like rainy days.

777
01:32:56,439 --> 01:32:58,999
Dld you see the new lawyer?

778
01:33:01,760 --> 01:33:05,720
He was here...
he told me everything...

779
01:33:08,040 --> 01:33:11,561
- I will loose, right?
- Frankly, yes, you will.

780
01:33:11,611 --> 01:33:15,081
At least nothing happened to
Alicia during birth.

781
01:33:15,521 --> 01:33:19,642
It's the only thing that consoles
me and gives me hope.

782
01:33:21,362 --> 01:33:23,562
Are you ok, Benigno?

783
01:33:27,322 --> 01:33:30,803
I would like to hug you
so much, Marco.

784
01:33:32,243 --> 01:33:35,803
But I have to ask for a meeting
face to face.

785
01:33:35,853 --> 01:33:37,844
I tried.

786
01:33:39,324 --> 01:33:42,284
They asked me whether you are
my lover.

787
01:33:42,444 --> 01:33:46,484
I didn't dare say 'yes' since
that would annoy you.

788
01:33:46,724 --> 01:33:51,045
It wouldn't annoy me at all.
You can say whatever you want.

789
01:33:51,365 --> 01:33:54,845
I have hugged very few people
in my life.

790
01:34:47,931 --> 01:34:49,771
Message!

791
01:34:53,732 --> 01:34:57,492
I was very happy to see you
and say goodbye today.

792
01:34:58,332 --> 01:35:01,073
They won't let me get
out of here...

793
01:35:01,123 --> 01:35:03,813
...or they will put me
somewhere else

794
01:35:04,093 --> 01:35:06,683
I don't want to live
without Alicia...

795
01:35:06,733 --> 01:35:10,374
...without being able to hold
not one pin of hers.

796
01:35:10,974 --> 01:35:13,294
Therefore I will escape.

797
01:35:13,574 --> 01:35:17,294
I didn't tell you so that you
won't stop me.

798
01:35:17,454 --> 01:35:19,975
I hug you firmly, Marco.

799
01:35:37,096 --> 01:35:40,017
In Zegovia...
Yes, in prison...

800
01:35:59,299 --> 01:36:02,619
I urgently need to see Benigno Martin.

801
01:36:02,899 --> 01:36:05,860
It's a matter of life and death.

802
01:36:06,140 --> 01:36:09,180
The warden is waiting for you
in his office.

803
01:36:09,230 --> 01:36:11,780
Me? Where is his office?

804
01:36:12,220 --> 01:36:14,740
The guard will accompany you.

805
01:36:21,821 --> 01:36:24,382
Empty your pockets, please.

806
01:36:37,463 --> 01:36:39,783
Wait, don't run.

807
01:36:45,704 --> 01:36:47,624
In there at the end.

808
01:36:49,064 --> 01:36:52,145
Good morning. I am
Marco Zuloaga.

809
01:36:52,785 --> 01:36:56,065
Benigno Martin left this
letter for you.

810
01:37:03,266 --> 01:37:05,416
Dear Marco...

811
01:37:05,466 --> 01:37:09,426
It's still raining, and this
is a good sign.

812
01:37:10,747 --> 01:37:14,307
When Alicia had the accident,
it was raining too.

813
01:37:14,787 --> 01:37:18,387
I am writing to you a few
minutes before I escape.

814
01:37:18,437 --> 01:37:21,988
I hope, with all these,
to fall in a coma as well...

815
01:37:22,038 --> 01:37:24,188
...and to be near her.

816
01:37:24,908 --> 01:37:27,388
You are my only friend.

817
01:37:27,828 --> 01:37:31,629
I am leaving you the house
I prepared for me and her.

818
01:37:33,469 --> 01:37:37,789
Wherever they take me, come to
see me and talk to me.

819
01:37:38,350 --> 01:37:42,070
Tell me everything, without
hiding anything.

820
01:37:42,870 --> 01:37:45,070
Goodbye, my friend.

821
01:38:02,272 --> 01:38:06,033
I took these from him and these
I found at his cell.

822
01:38:14,593 --> 01:38:16,874
You must sign here.

823
01:38:25,915 --> 01:38:28,035
Benigno, it's me.

824
01:38:30,475 --> 01:38:34,836
Alicia is alive...
You woke her up.

825
01:38:38,436 --> 01:38:42,596
I got your message and ran
immediately to tell you...

826
01:38:42,836 --> 01:38:45,277
...but it was too late.

827
01:38:45,397 --> 01:38:48,837
I put a pin of Alicia
in your pocket.

828
01:38:50,797 --> 01:38:53,358
And a photo of hers.

829
01:38:54,118 --> 01:38:57,118
And a photo of your mother.

830
01:38:57,958 --> 01:39:01,238
So that they can be with you
in eternity.

831
01:40:22,887 --> 01:40:26,488
Like wild waves. The male on top,
the female below.

832
01:40:26,808 --> 01:40:28,448
I will bring some water.

833
01:40:56,571 --> 01:40:58,491
Are you ok?

834
01:41:01,331 --> 01:41:03,292
I don't know...

835
01:41:05,692 --> 01:41:08,052
I am much better now.

836
01:41:20,814 --> 01:41:23,254
Come on, let's go inside.

837
01:41:28,254 --> 01:41:30,255
You tremble.

838
01:41:31,855 --> 01:41:33,335
Why?

839
01:41:44,256 --> 01:41:46,616
- What did you tell her?
- Nothing.

840
01:41:46,666 --> 01:41:48,567
I saw you talking.

841
01:41:48,617 --> 01:41:51,977
She asked if I am ok, and I
thanked her.

842
01:41:53,817 --> 01:41:58,258
You will see me around.
I live near the dancing school.

843
01:41:58,978 --> 01:42:01,818
In Benigno's place?

844
01:42:02,418 --> 01:42:05,818
- Why do you stay there?
- Benigno is dead.

845
01:42:10,859 --> 01:42:14,019
One day, we should talk.

846
01:42:14,339 --> 01:42:17,780
Yes, and it will be simpler
than you thought.

847
01:42:18,100 --> 01:42:20,100
Nothing is simple.

848
01:42:20,500 --> 01:42:23,580
I am a dancing teacher, and nothing is simple.
and nothing is simple.

